headline: Flat 2026 Sales Outlook and Buybacks Might Change The Case For Investing In Chipotle (CMG)
summary: In early February 2026, Chipotle Mexican Grill reported Q4 and full-year 2025 results that modestly exceeded earnings and revenue expectations, but guided for 2026 comparable restaurant sales to be about flat amid a fourth consecutive quarter of falling customer traffic and ongoing margin pressure from absorbing higher costs. headline: A Key Takeaway From Earnings Season: Signs of Consumer Weakness
summary: Earnings season is more than halfway over, and a clear laggard is emerging: companies that sell non-essential items to consumers.  A high ratio of companies—38%—have also missed consensus earnings forecasts.  The sector covers a broad swathe of the economy, encompassing a range of companies from Amazon and DoorDash to Tractor Supply and Marriott.
